snippet.title: Apes.io Early Access LIVE NOW
snippet.description:
Apes.io is the latest game from Addicting Games. In it you play as an Ape wielding a magic wand, scour the world looking for upgrades to your weapon and take down other Apes in the process!

Play for free at: http://apes.io
